Open terminal in project root:

1.Create virtual env and install deps:

python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate        # Linux / Mac
# .\venv\Scripts\activate      # Windows PowerShell
pip install --upgrade pip
pip install pandas scikit-learn flask joblib


2.Build dataset (creates data/synthetic_urls.csv):

python src/build_dataset.py


3.Train model:

python src/train.py
# result: models/phish_model.joblib


4.Run the Flask demo:

python src/api.py
# open http://127.0.0.1:5000 in your browser


5.Test with sample URLs:

Benign: https://www.google.com/search?q=hello

Suspicious: http://login-abc123-paypal.com/verify
